track_notes: Kleine Wanderung 5min längerer Weg von der Dosse auf die Rigi Scheidegg

Beautiful summer trail from a station of the cog railway train from Arth-Goldau (railway station and car park from nearby highway A4). Famous Felsenweg in the central part, a solid trail in the wall between First (restaurant) and Unterstetten with great view on the Lake of Lucerne. Steep ascent to the summit; both tracks (east/west) to the summit are not cleared in the winter period. The eastern track from Rigi Scheidegg is easier in winter.
track_title: Ascent from cog railway station Rigi Wölfertschen-First

track_notes: The trail head Rigi Kaltbad is a station of the other cog railway from Vitznau (car park, bus, boat). It is additionally accessible by cablecar from Weggis (car park, bus, boat/walk). Joins the other trail at Rigi First (restaurant). Alternative trail for Felsenweg (if closed) between First and Unterstetten (restaurant). Steep ascent to the summit; both tracks (east/west) to the summit are not cleared in the winter period. The eastern track from Rigi Scheidegg is easier in winter.
track_title: Ascent from cog railway station Rigi Kaltbad

track_notes: Pleasant hike from a first activation on Rigi Kulm along the ridge down to Unterstetten and up again to Dossen. Beautiful views, but takes its time.
track_title: Transit from Rigi Kulm, HB/SZ-021, on a summer trail
